            "description": "Expect 401 when WEBHOOK_USER is set in .env, and 200 when it is blank.\n\nIt is currently BLANK — webhook auth is disabled to match the device, which was set to httpAuthenticationMethod=none via the web UI. So this returns 200 today. Run 'npm run register' to turn auth back on at both ends."
          },
